\[\mathbf{P} \mathbf{i} = \begin{pmatrix} 0 \\ 0 \\ 0 \end{pmatrix}, \quad \mathbf{P} \mathbf{j} = \begin{pmatrix} 0 \\ 1 \\ 0 \end{pmatrix}, \quad \mathbf{P} \mathbf{k} = \begin{pmatrix} 0 \\ 0 \\ 0 \end{pmatrix},\]so
